                    <h1>Dextra 2014<hr /></h1>
                    <p>As Said by Bharat Ratna Dr.A.P.J Abdul Kalam, “Great dreams of great dreamers are always transcended ”.. Similar was the insight of bringing the best from the youth on a common scaffold when we started our journey by the name of Dextra in 2009.</p>
                    <p>Competition amongst students from across state and India being extremely overwhleming, display of voracious technology, motivational speeches to inspire the youth, and workshops to sharpen their skills, Dextra today is intimating platform that students across India can look up to.</p>
                    <p>With Many spellbinding events covering all genres of technology and management, Dextra brings some of the best conceptions for the mankind to the forefront . The huge amount of prize money is just another epitome of the heights we have scaled in the last three years</p>
                    <p>From workshops and guest lectures on the one hand to debates, quizzes and professional shows on the other, Dextra’2014 is playing host to a gamut of activities with spectrum of challenges for the brightest minds to test their capacity to ideate, drive their hunger to innovate and challenge their potential to fabricate new ideals like never before. Dextra’14 is all set to make you throe your grey cells and touch new horizons of ingenuity and innovation. Be it the magnanimous competitions that incite sparks of passion or the thought provoking addresses that set you thinking or quite simply, a personal Eureka moment amidst the deluge of ideas all around - Dextra has it all.</p>
                    <p>Carrying on with the legacy passed on to it, Dextra 2014 assures to provide you with the best twinkle of your life from the - to - . Filled with exciting and enamored workshops, guest lectures and exhibitions, along with the technological exaltation, Dextra provides the perfect assortment of learning and fun.</p>
